<section>
 <subtitle>no_params / hook_prompt</subtitle>
 <p>Enabling <em style="strong">no_params</em> will avoid the input window when rolling out a
 teplate.</p>

 <p>If disabled, <em style="strong">hook_prompt</em> will keep input fields pop up as GUI windows.
 Else you would get CLI prompts from cookiecutter directly.</p>
</section>

  




  



